10 REM ULA2 COLOR RAM DEMO
20 CLS
30 PRINT"*** ULA2 COLOR RAM DEMO ***"
40 PRINT
50 PRINT"HELLO WORLD IN COLORS!"
60 PRINT
70 PRINT"EACH CELL HAS ITS OWN"
80 PRINT"INK AND PAPER COLOR."
90 PRINT
100 REM COLOR RAM AT $B000 = 45056
110 REM FORMAT: INK(0-7) + PAPER(0-7)*8
120 REM ROW 4 = OFFSET 4*40 = 160
130 REM "HELLO WORLD IN COLORS!"
140 FOR I=0 TO 21
150 C=I-INT(I/7)*7+1
160 POKE 45056+160+I,C+0*8
170 NEXT I
180 REM ROW 6-7: COLORED BLOCKS
190 FOR I=0 TO 39
200 C=I-INT(I/7)*7
210 POKE 45056+240+I,7+C*8
220 POKE 45056+280+I,C+0*8
230 NEXT I
240 FOR I=0 TO 39
250 POKE 48768+240+I,32
260 POKE 48768+280+I,160
270 NEXT I
280 PRINT
290 PRINT
300 PRINT
310 PRINT"NO WASTED ATTRIBUTE BYTES!"
320 PRINT"EVERY CELL RENDERS DATA."
330 PRINT
340 PRINT"PRESS ANY KEY"
